line_1: What laws invented to keep under
line_2: People inclin'd to theft and plunder.
But tell me now, in Name of Wonder,

line_1: To keep ev'n Mons's Victor under:
line_2: Shall fright the World with impious Thunder.

line_1: Why they put so much Money the Candlestick under,
line_2: So they win to be sure; yet I very much wonder
For near a Minute, There's a wonder!
